snippet.title: A Glorious Return | Exandria Unlimited | Episode 3
snippet.description:
This episode is sponsored by Ravensburger. Check out the Taco Bell Party Pack Card Game at https://bit.ly/TacoBellGameNight

This episode is also sponsored by Idle Champions of the Forgotten Realms. Check out Idle Champions of the Forgotten Realms at http://IdleChampions.com/criticalrole.

The group must return to Emon to seek the expertise of a powerful runechild, but the seeming simplicity of this task is made more complicated by the Nameless Ones' relentless pursuit...

Watch Exandria Unlimited Thursdays at 7pm PT on https://twitch.tv/criticalrole and https://youtube.com/criticalrole. 

Meet the Players!
Game Master Aabria Iyengar
Aimee Carrero
Robbie Daymond
Ashley Johnson
Matthew Mercer
Liam O'Brien

Original Music by Omar Fadel and Hexany Audio
Main theme by Colm R. McGuinness
Additional music by Universal Production Music and Epidemic Sound
Character art by Hannah Friederichs 
Stained glass art by Joanna Johnen 
Opening Title by Christian Brown
Character Miniatures by Eldritch Foundry 
Miniatures painted by Ian Phillips
GM Screen by Dog Might

Due to the improv nature of RPG content on our channels, some themes and situations that occur in-game may be difficult for some to handle. If hearing discussions of certain episodes or scenes become uncomfortable, we strongly suggest taking a break or skipping that particular episode.
Your health and well-being is important to us and Psycom has a great list of international mental health resources, in case it’s useful: http://bit.ly/PsycomResources

Twitch subscribers gain instant access to VODs of our shows like Critical Role, Exandria Unlimited, and Critter Hug. But don't worry: Twitch broadcasts will be uploaded to YouTube about 36 hours after airing live, with audio-only podcast versions of select shows on  Spotify, iTunes, & Google Play following a week after the initial air date. Twitch subscribers also gain access to our official custom emote set and subscriber badges and the ability to post links in Twitch chat!

Follow us!
Website: https://www.critrole.com
Newsletter: https://critrole.com/newsletter
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/criticalrole
Twitter: https://twitter.com/criticalrole
Instagram: https://instagram.com/critical_role
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/criticalrole

Shops:

CA: https://canada.critrole.com
